ote><br />\nP.S. 所以警察會搵人好正常，佢地理撚得你屈對方錢定你送錢比對方，總之唔搞佢地就得"},{"pid":"3bfa2ca95d4b88b3d9de0e87769fe088a935fcc0","tid":118340,"uid":62320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗盲反到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難得蝗國有啲好人好事<br />\n就要講到係做show 講風涼說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個一碌鳩打沉一船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩好撚大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n究竟有幾撚多小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢多衰野你點反都得 <br />\n但唔好一又好野就話點點點<br />\n唔好又屌 好就做show<br />\n你玩撚哂啦連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：港獨撚"},{"pid":"996ac7795bbf7ec8ed44a27e13b5daeb28e81247","tid":118340,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"睇緊既時候已經估緊啲留言會幾偏激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03272ac6fbbaa6e8b9c08759fd7fe53af9239c8b","tid":118340,"uid":69606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:55:47.000Z","msg":"點解一開始就知係叔叔，唔係先生/女士。。。"},{"pid":"001269dbfa855e24b16a351dacf13dc4ab2a5b3b","tid":118340,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗盲反到咁<img src=\"/asset